<body>
  <div class="paper">
<pre>Dear von Neumann,

        You are right that August-September is
a vacation period here.  The vacations begin
about July 18.  I am very sorry that a talk
at our Colloquium therefore is out of question.
However, I shall be delighted to see you
personally.  I shall be in town from August
20th until the beginning of the Amsterdam
congress.

                    Yours most cordially
</pre>
  </div>
